    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>Monkey Do!</i></strong> introduces Mak, a mischievous monkey trapped in the run-down, Tropic Corp., zoo. After the Tropico family replaced all zoo workers with soulless robot Keepers, Mak knew it was time to break out.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >On his quest for freedom, he'll have to climb, leap, and zipline his way through the zoo. Using monkey stealth tactics, Mak can stay out of sight and gain the upper-hand. Trigger traps and using his trusty wrench, Mak can dismantle Keepers and earn scrap. Throughout the zoo's diverse habitat enclosures, he'll encounter a wide variety of animals. He'll need to gain their trust to acquire their assistance in his escape plan.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, the malicious zoo owners won't make things easy. Different type of robot Keepers and security systems will require Mak to use every ounce of his creativity to throw a real monkey wrench into the Tropic Corp. operation. The closer Mak gets to freedom the more the zoo descends into chaos.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/cab89b71774fb371ef11ea597edd670d.poster.avif?t=1765468392\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/cab89b71774fb371ef11ea597edd670d.webm?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/cab89b71774fb371ef11ea597edd670d.mp4?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HIDDEN MENACE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hiding in bins, lockers, hay stacks, and sneaking in tall grass is key for Mak to move about the zoo undetected and accomplish his goals.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/953979017d0d541af23a17f4091417b3.poster.avif?t=1765468392\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/953979017d0d541af23a17f4091417b3.webm?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/953979017d0d541af23a17f4091417b3.mp4?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MONKEY BUSINESS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climbing, leaping, using monkey bars and sliding on ziplines are just some of the ways Mak can move about the various zoo habitats with easy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/ba5da3a224f3eaacc39b3a5a8a425f36.poster.avif?t=1765468392\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/ba5da3a224f3eaacc39b3a5a8a425f36.webm?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/ba5da3a224f3eaacc39b3a5a8a425f36.mp4?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DISTRUPTIVE ANTICS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Using his upgradeable monkey wrench, Mak can dismantle unsuspecting robot Keepers, or he can luring them into traps to spring them when they least expect it.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/f073ad121125bbdd3c1f5ede80558e47.poster.avif?t=1765468392\" width=534 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/f073ad121125bbdd3c1f5ede80558e47.webm?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1763380/extras/f073ad121125bbdd3c1f5ede80558e47.mp4?t=1765468392\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >BEFRIENDING WILDLIFE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A variety of zoo animals can aid Mak in his perilous adventure, enabling him to reach new areas and battle against the insufferable Tropica family members. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is still in development so please keep checking back to this page for new features, content, and information!</p>",
